550
00:40:02,320 --> 00:40:03,119
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim, to je stvarnost.

551
00:40:03,840 --> 00:40:06,239
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, da, ako možete to učiniti s malim budžetom, sjajno.

552
00:40:06,400 --> 00:40:08,480
